.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"成日話人搞你內政<br />\n但係自己又成日搞鳩台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fe3c222d401c76b01c02b464fbe1f56b821bb0","tid":1653570,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"人地著咩嘢顏色嘅衫都要受共產黨審查"},{"pid":"d45617f9db7c1a881038b720cbcfa761a700cd94","tid":1653570,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"中國巨嬰最愛撒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ab0e3cad601d8b82507d63f64b2d977641e57a","tid":1653570,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"搞埋啲濕鳩條例<br />\n二百萬人一早叫你撤<br />\n搞到今時今日咁越演越烈<br />\n係到怪返示威者<br />\n咁當權者呢你班柒頭"},{"pid":"23fb9358f8702f6cc3516f803df3296f0960924b","tid":1653570,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"e? 有新詞語喎今次"},{"pid":"f85d9fe69a55e839fba1b96be8530971f9abcccd","tid":1653570,"uid":9217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"其實中共應該要多謝佢地<br />\n如果唔係佢地 都唔會咁多休息撚出黎叫人等法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee70941bf3b57e9a779ee9b9ed38c1985bf44f0","tid":1653570,"uid":59543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"多謝美國議員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536c3ec3dbca09904bf3264093364a43c5197c61","tid":1653570,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"口交左幾個月悶唔悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf734766b2be37f925d6b4e9fe87df7dcf8b983d","tid":1653570,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:31:49.000Z","