-<br />\n <br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"口交部let me recap in English. We love USA"},{"pid":"e70d7b640225167bf5c76d257bfde62d0696bad8","tid":1653570,"uid":301949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"脫下黑衣、收回黑手，停止插手香港事務，不得在中華民國的土地上撒野！<br />\n<br />\n我唔係好明佢想點"},{"pid":"143cfd3a4d8b404595822d6f8a64ba7e2a037fa9","tid":1653570,"uid":265389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"快啲鎖國，凍結美國人資產！唔做正契弟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c6b67337077ec3bd886a681b9a2ca4901f8016","tid":1653570,"uid":265389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e70d7b640225167bf5c76d257bfde62d0696bad8","tid":1653570,"uid":301949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"脫下黑衣、收回黑手，停止插手香港事務，不得在中華民國的土地上撒野！<br />\n<br />\n我唔係好明佢想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"要撒番大陸撒，除定衫等雜總，唔好將條洋腸益香林奠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bc82b4f614defbfc35725547b286b82e4d36cf","tid":1653570,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">包括香港同胞在內的中國人民</span>堅決反對克魯茲這樣撒謊成性的政客來港尋釁挑事...<br />\n<br />\n死撚開啦!!!支共口交部!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bd7ac00edc933ccb1b46d2981b91149a09548d","tid":1653570,"uid":107790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"多謝